##Bugs Fixed
JOB NOT FOUND - Railway was running multiple Gunicorn workers; each request could hit a different worker with no memory of the job. It was fixed by Claude Code dropping to 1 worker. 
"CONNECTION ERROR" on Agent 1- - Turned out being a stale Anthropic API key in Railway

