#Creative Lesson
I realised with this engine, that AI systems need just as much creative direction as us humans do. I made the mistake of not giving the agents enough creative guiding, so when I had Claude Code make sure Agent 1 behaved more as a "creative director" had the outputs become much more unique and appealing. 
As I have expressed before, AI isnt here to replace creativity-however-it needs genuine concise creative guidelines in order for it to help us execute the outcomes we want in the creative space. Which is exactly what I had done, only then was I happy with the results. 
